---
import Main from "../layouts/Main.astro";
import Linkbutton from "../components/Linkbutton.astro";
---

<Main title="Projects">
  <section class="grid_main">
    <div class="papayapicture">
      <video width="100%" height="100%" autoplay muted loop src="/projects/papaya.mp4"></video>
    </div>
    <div class="papayatext">
      <h2>Papaya summer</h2>
      <p>THE SPRING SUMMER 2023 COLLECTION COMES IN ALL Colours AND SHAPES. The collection addresses the diversity of different female bodies.</p>
      <div class="papayabutton">
        <Linkbutton href="/products" text="Shop here" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="voguetext">
      <h2>MERMAID DRESS IN VOGUE</h2>
      <p>“While it is not quite a time to bathe in the sun at the beach, it still dances on your skin through light crochet dresses in the archipelago” - VOGUE SCANDINAVIA</p>
      <div class="vougebutton">
        <Linkbutton href="/products" text="Shop the dress" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="vougepicture">
      <img src="/projects/vouge.webp" alt="Mermaid dress in vouge" />
    </div>
    <div class="iranpicture">
      <img src="/projects/iran.webp" alt="Voice of iran dress" />
    </div>
    <div class="irantext">
      <h2 class="dual-color">Voice of iran</h2>
      <h2>X LÜ ITEMS</h2>
      <p>VOICE OF IRAN x LÜ ITEMS supports Iranian Women's struggle for freedom. Like a thread in a skein of yarn, we are bound together in a world that senses the pain carried by women who live without freedom!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="iranbutton">
      <Linkbutton href="https://www.voiceofiran.dk/" text="SUPPORT VOICE OF IRAN" />
    </div>

    <div class="polhempicture">
      <img src="/projects/polhem.webp" alt="Items from polhem showroom" />
    </div>
    <div class="polhemtext">
      <h2>Polhem showroom</h2>
      <p>The Papaya summer collection is exhibited at the pr agency Polhem during the month of May.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Main>

<style>
  .papayapicture video {
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .grid_main {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    p,
    h2,
    .papayabutton,
    .vougebutton,
    .iranbutton {
      padding-inline-start: 8%;
      max-width: 90%;
    }

    .papayaptext {
      order: 1;
    }

    .papayatext h2 {
      width: 50%;
    }

    .papayapicture {
      order: 2;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
    .vougepicture {
      order: 2;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
    .voguetext {
      order: 4;
    }

    .iranpicture {
      order: 5;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
    .irantext {
      order: 6;
    }

    .dual-color {
      margin-bottom: 0;
      padding-top: 25px;
    }

    .irantext h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .iranbutton {
      order: 7;
    }
    .polhempicture {
      order: 8;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
    .polhemtext {
      order: 9;
    }
    .polhemtext h2 {
      width: 50%;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .grid_main {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .papayabutton {
      padding-top: 83%;
    }
    .voguetext p {
      padding-top: 50%;
    }
    .voguetext p {
      padding-top: 50%;
    }

    .voguetext h2 {
      position: absolute;
      width: 140%;
    }

    .vougebutton {
      padding-top: 58%;
      text-align: end;
    }
    .irantext p {
      width: 90%;
      padding-top: 20%;
    }

    .dual-color::first-line {
      color: #fcf6ac;
    }

    .dual-color {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 250px;
    }
    .papayapicture {
      grid-area: 1 / 1 / 2 / 2;
    }
    .papayatext {
      grid-area: 1 / 2 / 2 / 2;
      padding-inline-start: 25px;
      width: 90%;
    }
    .voguetext {
      grid-area: 2 / 1 / 2 / 2;
      position: relative;
      padding-inline-start: 25px;
      width: 90%;
    }

    .voguepicture {
      grid-area: 2 / 2 / 2 /2;
    }

    .iranpicture {
      margin-top: 3%;
      grid-area: 3 / 1 /3/3;
    }
    .irantext {
      position: relative;
      grid-area: 4 / 1 / 4 / 1;
      width: 100%;
      padding-inline-start: 25px;
    }
    .irantext h2 {
      margin: 0;
      position: absolute;
    }
    .iranbutton {
      grid-area: 4 / 2 / 4 / 3;
      justify-self: end;
      margin-inline-end: 25px;
    }
    .polhemtext {
      grid-area: 5 / 2 / 5 / 2;
      padding-inline-start: 25px;
      width: 90%;
    }
    .polhempicture {
      padding-top: 8%;
      grid-area: 5 / 1 / 5 / 1;
    }
  }
</style>
